import React from 'react'
import {BrowserRouter,Routers,Route} from 'ract-router-dom'
import Categores from './Categores'
import Categore from './Categore'
function RouterCategores() {
  return (
  <BrowserRouter>
   <Routers>
    <Route index element={<Categores/>}/>
    <Route path='/' element={<Categore/>}/>
   </Routers>
  </BrowserRouter>
  )
}

export default RouterCategores
